Review control description: (a) The Domestic Covered Entity shall undertake a legal review and document
the basis for identifying a jurisdiction where close-out netting and/or collateral
arrangements are not legally enforceable;

Review control description: (a) The model shall capture all relevant risk factors which materially influence the
NCCD contracts and reflect the nature, scale and complexity of the risks
inherent in the NCCD contracts;

Review control description: (b) The model shall calculate an estimate of the potential future exposure of
NCCD contracts, based on a one-tailed 99 per cent confidence interval over
a 10-day time horizon;
